OL,3,CEnergy firms to offer 'zero standing
OL,4,Ccharge' tariffs under Ofgem plans
OL,6,FUnder Ofgem's price cap, standing
OL,7,Fcharges have risen by 43% since 2019,
OL,8,Fand from January will cost dual fuel
OL,9,Fhouseholds an average of #338 a year,
OL,10,Falthough they disproportionately
OL,11,Faffect those who use less energy as
OL,12,Fthe fixed costs make up a higher
OL,13,Fproportion of their overall bill.
