OL,3,CEnergy firms to offer 'zero standing
OL,4,Ccharge' tariffs under Ofgem plans
OL,6,FSince October 1, households on a
OL,7,Fstandard variable tariff that pay for
OL,8,Ftheir electricity by direct debit have
OL,9,Fpaid on average 24.5p per unit, with a
OL,10,Fstanding charge of 60.99p per day. For
OL,11,Fgas, the average has been 6.24p per
OL,12,Funit with a standing charge of 31.66p
OL,13,Fper day.
OL,15,FFrom January 1, average standing
OL,16,Fcharges will decrease slightly to
OL,17,F60.97p per day for electricity and
OL,18,F31.65p per day for gas.
