OL,6,FOfgem also set out plans for a "debt
OL,7,Fguarantee" to improve the standard of
OL,8,Fservice offered by suppliers
OL,9,Fsupporting customers in debt, which it
OL,10,Fsaid would give households
OL,11,F"consistent, compassionate and
OL,12,Ftailored support".
OL,14,FSuppliers could also be required to
OL,15,Faccept debt repayment offers from
OL,16,Freputable third parties such as debt
OL,17,Fadvice agencies or consumer
OL,18,Forganisations.
