OL,6,F"Many people feel very strongly that
OL,7,Fstanding charges are unfair and
OL,8,Fprevent them from being able to manage
OL,9,Ftheir bills effectively.
OL,11,F"We want to give consumers the ability
OL,12,Fto make the choice that's right for
OL,13,Fthem without putting any one group of
OL,14,Fconsumers at a disadvantage. And by
OL,15,Fhaving a zero standing charge tariff,
OL,16,Fwe would create that choice for
OL,17,Feveryone."
