OL,7,Fenergy debt is the second-most common
OL,8,Fdebt among people it helps ` behind
OL,9,Fcredit cards ` with the average amount
OL,10,Fowed in energy arrears increasing by
OL,11,F37% in the past year to #1,541.
OL,13,FNational Energy Action said Ofgem's
OL,14,F"lack of any significant reform" of
OL,15,Fstanding charges was "extremely
OL,16,Fdisappointing".
