OL,6,FThe charity's director of policy and
OL,7,Fadvocacy, Peter Smith, said: "There is
OL,8,Fsignificant public concern around how
OL,9,Fhigh standing charges are. All major
OL,10,Fpolitical parties made promises in
OL,11,Ftheir manifestos to reduce standing
OL,12,Fcharges.
OL,14,F"Households that use prepayment meters
OL,15,Fare particularly impacted by the
OL,16,Fcontinuation of high standing charges.
OL,17,FWhile several options to better
OL,18,Fprotect prepayment meter households
OL,19,Fhave been identified, Ofgem has opted
OL,20,Fto do nothing, leaving vulnerable
OL,21,Fhouseholds in often dire situations."
