OL,6,FCitizens Advice head of energy policy
OL,7,FAlex Belsham-Harris said: "We hear
OL,8,Ffrom people who've turned off their
OL,9,Fheating, ration their hot water, and
OL,10,Favoid charging essential mobility
OL,11,Fdevices, yet still feel like they're
OL,12,Ffighting a losing battle with their
OL,13,Fenergy bills.
OL,15,F"It's vital that changes to standing
OL,16,Fcharges avoid driving up bills for low-
OL,17,Fincome households who have higher
OL,18,Fenergy needs."
